        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Elemental Gift]</em></p>\n<p>An elemental force fills your target, granting the target the swiftness of air, the ruggedness of earth, the sting of fire, or the flexibility of water, depending on which element you choose. Choose an element when you Cast the Spell. The target gains the benefit of that element as described below, and this spell gains that trait's element.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Metal</strong> The target's Strikes using a metal weapon or an unarmed attack deal an additional 1d4 electricity damage on a hit and get a +1 status bonus to the attack roll if the target is made of metal or wearing metal armor.</li>\n</ul>"
